c powder",\n      "note": null,\n      "optional": false,\n      "group": "spice"\n    },\n    {\n      "amount": 0.25,\n      "unit": "tsp",\n      "item": "onion powder",\n      "note": null,\n      "optional": false,\n      "group": "spice"\n    },\n    {\n      "amount": 1,\n      "unit": "tsp",\n      "item": "pickle relish or pickles",\n      "note": "spooned from relish or pickles",\n      "optional": false,\n      "group": "acid"\n    },\n    {\n      "amount": 1,\n      "unit": "pinch",\n      "item": "salt",\n      "note": null,\n      "optional": false,\n      "group": "seasoning"\n    }\n  ],\n  "steps": [\n    {\n      "step_number": 1,\n      "instruction": "Combine all ingredients in a small bowl.",\n      "time_note": null,\n      "heat_note": null,\n      "equipment_note": "small bowl"\n    },\n    {\n      "step_number": 2,\n      "instruction": "Stir until the sauce is completely smooth and even.",\n      "time_note": null,\n      "heat_note": null,\n      "equipment_note": null\n    },\n    {\n      "step_number": 3,\n      "instruction": "Taste and adjust if needed with a little extra pickle-spoon for more acidity.",\n      "time_note": null,\n      "heat_note": null,\n      "equipment_note": null\n    },\n    {\n      "step_number": 4,\n      "instruction": "Chill in the refrigerator for at least 30 minutes before serving so the flavors can settle.",\n      "time_note": "30 min minimum",\n      "heat_note": null,\n      "equipment_note": "refrigerator"\n    }\n  ],\n  "recipe_notes": "I rewrote the recipe into a compact journal format that fits the fields in your Moleskine book. I kept the content essentially unchanged, but made the method tighter and more natural for handwritten transfer on the page.",\n  "service_notes": "Big Mac-inspired sauce. Tangy, sweet and creamy. Good for burgers, fries and wraps.",\n  "source_type": "markdown_file",\n  "source_url": null,\n  "raw_source_text": "Kategori: Sauces / Condiments\n\nRecipe: Burgarsås\n\nNote: Big Mac-inspirerad sås. Syrlig, söt och krämig. Bra till burgare, pommes och wraps.\n\nDifficulty: Enkel\nIngredients: 1 dl majonnäs, 1 msk söt gurkrelish, 2 tsk gul senap, 1 tsk vitvinsvinäger, 1/2 tsk paprikapulver, 1/4 tsk vitlökpulver, 1/4 tsk lökpulver, 1 tsk spad från relish eller pickles, 1 nypa salt.\n\nServes: 2 burgare\nPreparation time: 10 min + vila\nCooking time: 0 min\nCooking process: Rörs kall\nWine pairing: Lätt pinot noir eller zinfandel\nRating: ☆☆☆☆☆\n\nPreparation:\nBlanda alla ingredienser i en liten skål. Rör tills såsen är helt slät och jämn. Smaka av och justera vid behov med lite extra pickle-spad för mer syra. Ställ i kylen minst 30 minuter före servering så att smaken hinner sätta sig.\n\nVad jag ändrade och varför:\nJag skrev om receptet till ett kompakt journalformat som passar fälten i din Moleskine-bok. Jag behöll innehållet i princip oförändrat, men gjorde metoden tätare och mer naturlig för handskriven överföring på sidan.",\n  "uncertainty_notes": [\n    "Source language is Swedish; all normalized fields are in English.",\n    "Wine pairing note is in Swedish and not translated to preserve raw source meaning.",\n    "Difficulty is listed as 'Enkel' (Swedish for 'Easy') but normalized to 'easy' in complexity field.",\n    "Cooking process 'Rörs kall' (Swedish for 'Stir cold') is interpreted as cold preparation technique.",\n    "Rating is shown as five stars but not translated or normalized to a numeric value.",\n    "Yield is given as '2 burgare' (Swedish for '2 burgers') and normalized to '2 burgers' in yield_text.",\n    "Prep time includes '10 min + vila' (Swedish for 'rest') which is interpreted as 10 minutes prep plus chilling time.",\n    "Total time is calculated as 10 minutes prep + 30 minutes chilling = 40 minutes total.",\n    "Ingredient 'spad' is a Swedish colloquialism for 'spoon' and normalized to 'spooned' in note.",\n    "Ingredient 'gurkrelish' is a Swedish misspelling of 'pickle relish' and normalized to 'sweet